name: Alexa Johnson
summary: Alexa Johnson is a 32-year-old, non-binary, software developer living in Los Angeles. They are originally from Boston and graduated from Harvard University. They speak English and Spanish. They are an African descent and have an ITPN personality type, self-identifying as liberal and atheist. Although they don't currently have any children, they do aspire to in the future. Alexa has a pet dog, enjoys coding, reading, and hiking. They exercise regularly and occasionally enjoy a drink but don't smoke nor use drugs. They're interested in monogamous, long-term relationships with someone ages 30-40, who likewise values fitness, doesn't smoke, and wants children in future.
